'''Tawsit''' ([[asget]]: ''tiwsitin'') d [[Adras amessarti]] n unagi neɣ n unadi deg [[tsertut tusnant n telmas|tasartut tusnant n telmas]] yeɣɣaren deg waɛas n [[Amuddir|imuddiren]] yettemcabin deg talɣa d uẓaṛ.

== Assissen ==
Akk [[talmest|tilmas]] n [[Amuddir|imuddiren]] ([[aɣersiw]], [[tuga]], [[imɣan]], [[agersal|igersalen]]...) ttwaqqnen ar yiwet n tewsit, ɣef uguni n [[isem usnan|yisem usnan]] yettwassissenen sɣur [[Carl von Linné]].

Yal talmest tezmer ad tesɛu aṭas [[adu-talmest|adu-tilmas]]: [[tuggta (tazegzawt)|tuggtiwin]] neɣ [[talɣa (tazegzawt)|talɣiwin]]. S umedya, [[awerɣil amenkad]] (isem alatini : ''Aptenodytes forsteri'') d [[awerɣil ageldan|uwerɣil ageldan]] (''Aptenodytes patagonica'') llan sin yidsen deg tewsit ''Aptenodytes'', n [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n sapiens [[awerɣil|iwerɣilen]].

Tawsit talsant semman-as [[Homo]].

